  <div class="hero-foot reveal">
    <p class="hero-bio">
      I build <em>AI products for boring industries</em>. Right now that's Maya AI at ESC Partners, a customer-support assistant for utility companies. Before this I founded two companies in the UK and Middle East and sold both. <em>Two exits. $575K combined.</em> Then a master's in AI at Simon Business School.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-meta">
      <div>Currently<b>AI PM, ESC Partners</b></div>
      <div>Based<b>Rochester, NY</b></div>
